(36, '%s is a network of globally distributed servers that cache content and deliver it to your website visitors faster based on their location, reducing website load times and improving performance. This technology is also known as a content delivery network (CDN). {{strong}}Servers may also be located in countries that are considered unsafe in terms of data protection law.{{/strong}}', '', 'real-cookie-banner', 0, 36, 0),
